  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Bespin_-_Ground",
  "title": "Battle of Bespin -- Ground",
  "summary": "As the New Republic's main force arrives over Bespin and demands the Imperial occupiers surrender, a Republic ground team sets out to plant explosives along Cloud City's causeways, pipelines, and control centers. The raider Gene leads the demolition push while Imperial defenders -- the recalled scout Crewman Sev'rance Cassoni, the precise medic-soldier Galatea, 2nd Lt. Malantean, the trooper Calyx Drogyn (TK-4462), Chool, and Private Ndresi of the 501st -- move to intercept across the platform. A vicious firefight erupts: Gene dives from cover to cover under concentrated fire, methodically setting his charges, while Galatea and Cassoni return disciplined volleys and Chool's shooting forces the Republic officer to duck. The Imperials take a beating -- Drogyn is wounded and the officer hard-pressed -- and once all the explosives are placed Gene calls for the team to fall back. As the fight ebbs, Galatea drops her aim to perform frantic field triage on a downed comrade, and the troopers prep their wounded for evacuation under covering fire.",
